         <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Interview with Charlie Cole, 2020-10-26</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
         <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>We switched to an evacuation rescue mode to where the police and the fire, all the first responders, all the additional resources switched over to an evacuation and rescue mode. We actually, the numbers say, that we evacuated 14,000, approximately, people in Gatlinburg surrounding area of the county and Gatlinburg area that night.</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:01:02"
                            endTime="00:01:57">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q1</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Can you state your name and tell us about your background?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 1</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
