         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:01:57"
                            endTime="00:03:17">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q2</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Outside of your work with the fire department, can you talk about your involvement with the community?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 2</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:03:17"
                            endTime="00:04:46">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q3</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What were your experiences in the days and weeks leading up to the wildfires in 2016?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 3</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:04:46"
                            endTime="00:06:03">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q4</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>When were you first notified about the fire on Chimney Tops?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 4</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:06:03"
                            endTime="00:07:17">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q5</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>So there was a lot of smoke on the day of the fire? At what point were you concerned that the fire could come into the city?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 5</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:07:17"
                            endTime="00:08:53">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q6</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>In your role at that time, what were the operational logistics or activities that you were undertaking that day?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 6</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:08:53"
                            endTime="00:10:45">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q7</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What transpired when you and your colleagues first realized the wildfires were entering Gatlinburg?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 7</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:10:45"
                            endTime="00:13:26">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q8</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What happened as the fire started coming out of Twin Creeks and into Gatlinburg? Could you talk about the direction the fire ended up taking?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 8</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:13:26"
                            endTime="00:14:42">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q9</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What were your experiences that evening as the fire progressed and communications began with other fire departments that came into the city?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 9</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:14:42"
                            endTime="00:15:27">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q10</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Were you based at the fire department that evening or somewhere else?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 10</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:15:27"
                            endTime="00:17:27">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q11</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What was it like at the command center? What were some personal feelings from that night you felt as a resident of Gatlinburg?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 11</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:17:27"
                            endTime="00:19:03">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q12</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Are there any memories from that evening that have stuck with you?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 12</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:19:03"
                            endTime="00:20:39">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q13</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>What transpired as the night went on? What kind of direction was given to the fire department?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 13</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:20:39"
                            endTime="00:22:24">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q14</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>How did the weather shift that night? When the rain came, what transpired next?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 14</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
         <pbcore:pbcorePart partType="Interview Questions"
                            startTime="00:22:24"
                            endTime="00:23:46">
            <pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier source="local">20201026_Cole_Charlie_Q15</pbcore:pbcoreIdentifier>
            <pbcore:pbcoreTitle>Were there other urgent issues besides evacuation that you dealt with that evening?</pbcore:pbcoreTitle>
            <pbcore:pbcoreDescription>Question 15</pbcore:pbcoreDescription>
         </pbcore:pbcorePart>
